Geschichte
The band was founded in 1987. In 1989 the first EP followed called Born for War on WEA Records. Following the publication was followed by appearances with Onslaught, Acid Reign, Xentrix, Toranaga and Celtic Frost. After the release of their debut album followed The Work of Idle Handsâ€¦. Later, the band split again by their label and signed a contract with Heavy Metal Records. In the EP Insanity Addicts followed at the label. In 1991 the second album Nightmare Scenario.
